  "about": {
    "eyebrow": "Local since day one",
    "headline": "A homegrown band playing in the Hudson Valley.",
    "lead": "A local Hudson Valley band formed in 2017, covering the top bands, artists and one-hit wonders over the past several decades!",
    "body": "Our song selections focus on harmony-based hits, that cut across all generations and will have you singing along and swaying to the beat of your favorite classic songs from the 60’s, 70’s,80’s and 90’s!!\n\nThe group was built around three sisters, who have been singing and harmonizing with each other since childhood, along with guitar, keyboards, bass, drums and vocalist accompaniment.",
